# 13. Interpreting Attention Scores

Example:

```
[[0.50 0.30 0.20]
 [0.20 0.60 0.20]
 [0.10 0.25 0.65]]
```

Interpretation:

Token 1 attends mostly to itself.

Token 2 attends mostly to itself.

Token 3 attends strongly to itself.

Higher values indicate stronger attention.

